Oodaadunnon rogaarishdan gehabhrashdan
Mithrangall than chaare chellaan paadillaatthon

Thallllappetton duà´ƒkhemagnan kettaanannaall
Vaidyan yeshukristhan cheyyum saahaayangall

Thaathangkal ninnanpodundaay, kelppum thaangum
Paarinnettam poorippikkum kaarunyaabdhe

Srshdi sthothram poornnathvam poondillennaalum
Sthothratthil nee modikkunnu naathhaa! Sthothram.
